  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/item_id-695342__notification_id-1061886\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/item_id-695342__notification_id-1061886\">原問題</a><br/>\n<br/>\n我在跟一位韓裔說了同樣的事情後，他說，Robert這怎麼了，還有兩個旗子可以選呢，<br/>\n<br/>\n韓國人以前只能掛日本旗 （好像他說得很有道理啊）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWM5NjI5ZWI4NTBiOTFkZTI1MzI3LnBuZz93aWR0aD05NzImaGVpZ2h0PTcwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5c9629eb850b91de25327.png?width=972&amp;height=700\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5c9629eb850b91de25327.png?width=972&amp;height=700\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5c9629eb850b91de25327.png?width=972&amp;height=700\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n1936年，柏林奧運會<br/>\n<br/>\n這個時候我想起來了Igor Sikorsky，明明是烏克蘭人，但是烏克蘭普遍不被當作一個國家，所以以前大多數時候被算成俄國人<br/>\n<br/>\n然後還有Danzig居民裡的Kashubians人，Galicia人等等<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n品蔥上的上海人可以把International Settlement的旗子拿出來了<br/>\n然後別忘了把Prussia也放進來<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTA4YmQwYjFkNDY1OGQyYjgyZjNiLmpwZz93aWR0aD0zNzUwJmhlaWdodD0xODc1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/908bd0b1d4658d2b82f3b.jpg?width=3750&amp;height=1875\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/908bd0b1d4658d2b82f3b.jpg?width=3750&amp;height=1875\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/908bd0b1d4658d2b82f3b.jpg?width=3750&amp;height=1875\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
